org.smtlib.impl

Class Sort.FcnSort

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.smtlib.impl.Pos.Posable
      • org.smtlib.impl.Sort
        • org.smtlib.impl.Sort.FcnSort
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAccept, IPos.IPosable, ISort, ISort.IFcnSort
    Enclosing class:
    Sort

    public static class Sort.FcnSort
extends Sort
implements ISort.IFcnSort
    Represents the class of the sort of a function symbol. This is not a sort that can be expressed in SMT-LIB sort grammar, except implicitly when function ids are defined in define-fun and declare-fun commands and in theory definitions.
